message:
Looking for a subleaser for the summer! Dinkytown apartment, $585 rent for your own room, or share it for $293.75. Wifi and electric together cost about $35/month, laundry room is in basement of building. Fully furnished (unless you want to share the room, then one person would need to bring a bed).

Great community living here, there are 4 CRU apartment units at this location, so always someone who loves Jesus and can hang out right next door! 

Message if interested. :)
